metadata.name: wavWRLD presents: wavROOM feat. AbJo
metadata.description:
The wavROOM experiences are token-curated intimate performances only open to the collectors of that artist. This 6-of-7 performance is with the legendary Producer, DJ & Musician, AbJo of Soulection.

These are the first live music performances minted on the blockchain.

wavWRLD partnered with Glass.xyz & Reveel to record & mint the performances.

Video, Editing & Color by LadiDadi @ladidadilive
Audio, Mix & Master by Invictus @theoginvictus
